item.description:
@gothic_queen wrote:

[quote=“Bebemycat2, post:14, topic:123703”][quote author=Casey. link=topic=173502.msg1600569#msg1600569 date=1184571596]

So basically you’re making a raft so you can sink it then get a ride in a coast guard helicopter? And I thought putting smoke bombs in my neighbors mailbox was cool…

If you make it right and it covers enough surface area then it should displace you weight and be atleast somewhat buoyant. If you plan on sinking it, just make a sort of removable board in the middle so you can take it out, and water floods in and down goes the “boat”.

That is cool.

We’re actually trying to do a knock of from viva la bam kinda thing, Summer is almost over and we wanna do something fun.
Our goal is to get to one of those boat restrants(firefox won’t give me correct spelling-.-), we’re you bring your boat in, and you go eat.
[/quote]
Lol, I live like 30 minutes from where that episode was filmed
I have seen Bam and some of the others from the Jackass/CKY crew… I have actually seen Bam’s old house, but not his new one :([/quote]
Ay lucky!

We might do the hotdog thing, in the research I’ve done, it will get water logged or w/e, and eventually sink.
Oh new episode of Hannah Montana
Well I think I’ve got my answers, thanks for the help
